These are Puzzles for 5x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, october, april, january, may
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, scientist, police-officer, engineer, freelancer
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, dancing, gardening, reading, writing
House: gothic-revival, victorian, wooden, modern, palace
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, green, aquamarine, white, pink
 1. the palace house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the engineer##1
 3. the police-officer is on the left of the teacher##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the modern house is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who likes pink##1
10. the modern house is the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the palace house is on the left of the wooden house##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the palace house##1
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
14. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
15. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the teacher##1
16. the scientist is between the person who likes green and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3    |    4     |      5      |
| Birthday      | may     | march          | october   | april | january    |
| Job          | police-officer  | teacher        | freelancer | scientist   | engineer |
| Hobby         | chess   | dancing       | reading | writing  | gardening   |
| House   | victorian  | modern     | palace | wooden  | gothic-revival    |
| Color         | aquamarine | white | green   | lilac     | pink      |

