.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, amaryllis, aconite, zinnia, sunflower
5 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, go, bridge, backgammon
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, peas, pumpkin, tomato, orange
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, handball, rowing, rugby, volleyball
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, cooking, woodworking, traveling, gardening
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 6. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person eating orange is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing go##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing domino##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
12. the person eating peas is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating peas##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsmarigold##2
16. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |     5      |
| Flower           | sunflower | aconite | marigold  | zinnia      | amaryllis |
