13. the person playing domino is the person who growsaconite##1
14. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
15. the person drinking water is between the person who growsdaffodil and the game-smoker##2
16. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
