The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, van, bike, airplane, motorbike
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, green, turquise, amber, emerald
5 different pets are kept: frog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is between the person driving the scooter and the person who's sport is rugby##2
 8. the person who likes green is the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the person driving the airplane is the person who likes emerald##1
12. the person who likes turquise is between the person traveling to prague and the person driving the airplane##2
13. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes yellow##1
14. the person who likes emerald is between the owner of the horse and the person driving the scooter##2
15. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |     4      |    5    |
